import Module from "../common/module";
import bytesFilter from "./bytes-filter";
import hertzFilter from "./hertz-filter";
import percentFilter from "./percent-filter";
import dateFilter from "./date-filter";
import trustAsHtml from "./trustAsHtml-filter";
import highlight from "./highlight-filter";
import unitConversionFilter from "./unit-conversion-filter";
 
export default (module:Module)=> {
    module.filter("xuiUnitConversion", unitConversionFilter);
    module.filter("xuiBytes", bytesFilter); // [DEPRECATED]
    module.filter("swBytes", bytesFilter); // [DEPRECATED]
    module.filter("xuiHertz", hertzFilter); // [DEPRECATED]
    module.filter("swPercent", percentFilter);
    module.filter("swDate", dateFilter);
    module.filter("xuiTrustAsHtml", trustAsHtml);
    module.filter("xuiHighlight", highlight);
};
